OL,3,CSenior doctors call for 'urgent
OL,4,Cintervention' at Noble's Hospital
OL,6,FSenior doctors and consultants at
OL,7,FNoble's Hospital are calling for
OL,8,F'immediate government intervention' to
OL,9,Fresolve a 'critical shortfall in
OL,10,Finpatient bed capacity' on the Isle of
OL,11,FMan.
OL,13,FA group of 75 members of senior staff
OL,14,Fheld a Medical Staff Committee (MSC)
OL,15,Fmeeting, outlining the concerns.
OL,17,FThe group says the hospital's current
OL,18,Fcapacity is 'insufficient to safely
OL,19,Fsupport the simultaneous demands of
OL,20,Femergency admissions and planned
OL,21,Fsurgical procedures'.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
