PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773667699
OL,3,CSenior doctors call for 'urgent
OL,4,Cintervention' at Noble's Hospital
OL,6,FIt claims Noble's Hospital operated
OL,7,Fwith 314 beds, before the formation of
OL,8,FManx Care in 2021.
OL,10,FThey say the hospital is currently
OL,11,Foperating with 168 beds, which is a
OL,12,F46% decrease in capacity.
OL,14,FIn addition to their statement, the
OL,15,FMSC said physicians are experiencing
OL,16,F"profound moral injury" and a "deep
OL,17,Fpsychological distress born from the
OL,18,Fsystemic gap between their
OL,19,Fprofessional ethics and the daily
OL,20,Foperational reality of the Isle of
OL,21,FMan's healthcare environment".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
