FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773667699
OL,3,CSenior doctors call for 'urgent
OL,4,Cintervention' at Noble's Hospital
OL,6,FIn a responding statement, a
OL,7,Fgovernment spokesperson says the
OL,8,Fminister for the Department of Health
OL,9,Fand Social Care met with the MSC, when
OL,10,Fconcerns where originally raised.
OL,12,FIt added: 'The department is committed
OL,13,Fto examine operational issues and
OL,14,Flooks forward to continuing the
OL,15,Fdialogue with clinicians to map a
OL,16,Fclear way forward.'
OL,18,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,19,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,20,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,21,Four region.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/3
